'''''Chimarrhis''''' is a [[genus]] of [[flowering plant]]s in the [[Family (biology)|family]] [[Rubiaceae]].<ref>[https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/page/303825#page/86/mode/1up Nicolaus Joseph von Jacquin. 1763. Selectarum Stirpium Americanarum Historia in qua ad Linnaeanum Systema Determinatae p 61]</ref> It has 15 recognized species, native to [[Central America]], [[South America]] and the [[West Indies]].<ref name="WCSP">{{cite web|url=http://apps.kew.org/wcsp/qsearch.do?plantName=Chimarrhis|title=''Chimarrhis'' in the World Checklist of Rubiaceae|accessdate=June 2014}}</ref>

